---
title: Cheat's Baked Double Chicken Dhal with Red Lentils & Silverbeet
description: No wonder dhal is the darling of Indian home cooking – it's nutritious, versatile, easy to make and brimming with flavour. Here,
we're adding tender pieces of chicken, versatile veggies and crunchy crushed peanuts.
